Name: Vole Complexity
About the game: VOLE COMPLEXITY is a Top-Down Puzzle-Game, which will boil your brain. Charlie, the vole got lost and is searching a way back home. Do you have what it takes to find the way through all the mazes which are getting more and more complex? Features ﻿ „Going Up?“ - It's the main mode of the game. Find the way out and bring Charlie back home. Three different skill levels with 10 Floors for each (30 in total) will demand everything from you! Collecting stars : Every maze has it's own specific minimum time and minimum steps you can theoretically make to beat the maze. If you find the fastest possible way through a maze you will earn a star which will unlock more achievments.
